<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 12:12:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列政府正在用资金消除绿线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-government-is-eliminating-the-green-line-with-money/0000018e-bcd4-d7ee-a39e-fdfebb870000</link><description>预算逐个预算，法律逐个法律：从强迫手机公司扩大在被占领土的覆盖范围到促进公共资金向定居点转移的法律。这就是内塔尼亚胡的极右政府正在努力实现事实上的吞并</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 12:06:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-government-is-eliminating-the-green-line-with-money/0000018e-bcd4-d7ee-a39e-fdfebb870000</guid></item><item><title>“把他们全部杀掉”：伊斯兰国威胁观看欧洲冠军联赛四分之一决赛的球迷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/kill-them-all-isis-threatens-fans-attending-uefa-champions-league-quarterfinal-matches/0000018e-c293-d6f4-afaf-eed397460000</link><description>在马德里，24小时内将进行两场比赛，这一威胁受到了认真对待。尽管该市安全官员明确表示无需恐慌，西班牙目前警戒级别为5级（共5级），为最高级别。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 12:02:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/kill-them-all-isis-threatens-fans-attending-uefa-champions-league-quarterfinal-matches/0000018e-c293-d6f4-afaf-eed397460000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其和以色列贸易针锋相对，关系进一步恶化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-09/ty-article/turkey-slams-israel-with-export-sanctions-until-gaza-cease-fire-achieved/0000018e-c25b-d6f4-afaf-ee5b08c00000</link><description>土耳其已经停止向以色列发送任何可用于军事目的的货物。以色列表示将通过限制从土耳其进口的产品来回应这些措施</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 11:11:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-09/ty-article/turkey-slams-israel-with-export-sanctions-until-gaza-cease-fire-achieved/0000018e-c25b-d6f4-afaf-ee5b08c00000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯赢了吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/has-hamas-won/0000018e-c21d-d1b7-a3af-e71f0f590000</link><description>哈马斯颠覆了以色列在军事上所向披靡的剧本，暴露了其国际支持的脆弱性，引发了对其长期可持续性的严峻质疑。西方、温和的阿拉伯国家、以色列和巴勒斯坦权力机构有责任阻止他们取得任何最终胜利</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 10:40:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/has-hamas-won/0000018e-c21d-d1b7-a3af-e71f0f590000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府报告显示，自 10 月 7 日和加沙战争以来，以色列收到的捐款已达 14 亿美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/donations-to-israel-since-oct-7-and-gaza-war-top-1-4-billion-israeli-govt-report-finds/0000018e-c219-d480-a99e-ce5f096c0000</link><description>新报告显示，这 14 亿美元中约有一半是由北美犹太联合会及其 146 个成员组织筹集的，大约 58,000 名志愿者从国外飞往以色列</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:41:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/donations-to-israel-since-oct-7-and-gaza-war-top-1-4-billion-israeli-govt-report-finds/0000018e-c219-d480-a99e-ce5f096c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长因法律困难否决本格维尔的警察发言人候选人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-vetoes-appointment-of-ben-gvirs-candidate-as-police-spokesperson/0000018e-c1b2-d6f4-afaf-edf2c6ca0000</link><description>消息人士称，如果国家安全部长批准提拔本-格维尔在警察内部的同僚，以色列警察局长同意聘请本-格维尔的候选人担任警察发言人</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 08:36:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-vetoes-appointment-of-ben-gvirs-candidate-as-police-spokesperson/0000018e-c1b2-d6f4-afaf-edf2c6ca0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军事演习缓解加沙压力，为人质谈判提供关键时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-maneuvers-ease-pressure-on-gaza-presenting-key-moment-for-hostage-talks/0000018e-bf36-d92b-adaf-ff763abc0000</link><description>以色列国防军从加沙南部撤军以及援助物资数量增加两倍可能有助于谈判，或者让辛瓦尔觉得不必着急，从而威胁到以色列脆弱的联盟。与此同时，哈马斯和巴勒斯坦权力机构为控制加沙剩余的民事机构进行了一场悄悄的战争</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 03:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-maneuvers-ease-pressure-on-gaza-presenting-key-moment-for-hostage-talks/0000018e-bf36-d92b-adaf-ff763abc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外长表示，埃尔多安对以色列实施出口禁运后，以色列将进行经济报复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article-live/naval-iron-dome-intercepts-target-over-red-sea-for-first-time-hamas-no-progress-on-talks/0000018e-c0a2-db65-a7af-d0aab8ef0000</link><description>法国、埃及、约旦领导人呼吁加沙“立即停火” ■ 哈马斯称以色列提议未能满足巴勒斯坦要求，将继续审查 ■ 内塔尼亚胡称拉法行动日期已定 ■ 白宫称释放人质协议已提交给巴勒斯坦哈马斯，等待回应；外国外交官表示，埃及关于加沙谈判取得进展的报道中存在“谨慎乐观”情绪</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 02:27:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article-live/naval-iron-dome-intercepts-target-over-red-sea-for-first-time-hamas-no-progress-on-talks/0000018e-c0a2-db65-a7af-d0aab8ef0000</guid></item><item><title>费城剧院因担心亲巴勒斯坦人的强烈反对而取消放映以色列电影</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/philadelphia-theater-nixes-screening-of-israeli-film-over-fear-of-pro-palestinian-backlash/0000018e-bfdc-db65-a7af-ffdcb9a70000</link><description>布林莫尔电影学院原定在费城举行的年度以色列电影节上放映一部关于以色列音乐家耶胡达·波利克 (Yehuda Poliker) 的纪录片，但在提前一天通知后就取消了该学院</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 22:54:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/philadelphia-theater-nixes-screening-of-israeli-film-over-fear-of-pro-palestinian-backlash/0000018e-bfdc-db65-a7af-ffdcb9a70000</guid></item><item><title>参议员伊丽莎白·沃伦：以色列在加沙的行动可能在法律上构成种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/sen-elizabeth-warren-israels-actions-in-gaza-may-legally-constitute-genocide/0000018e-bf87-d6f4-afaf-bfc7919d0000</link><description>尽管几名批评以色列的进步派众议院议员表示，他们个人认为这次军事行动构成了种族灭绝，但没有人敢直截了当地这么说。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 21:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/sen-elizabeth-warren-israels-actions-in-gaza-may-legally-constitute-genocide/0000018e-bf87-d6f4-afaf-bfc7919d0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔：最新提案将弥合人质谈判中的分歧；哈马斯否认进展报告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/qatar-latest-proposal-bridges-gaps-in-hostage-talks-hamas-denies-reports-of-progress/0000018e-bf65-d480-a99e-ff77153b0000</link><description>调解员等待以色列和哈马斯的回应；以色列消息人士称，协议要求哈马斯提供第一阶段释放的40名人质的姓名，并保证他们还活着，以换取原则上同意允许巴勒斯坦人返回加沙北部的家园</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 20:45:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/qatar-latest-proposal-bridges-gaps-in-hostage-talks-hamas-denies-reports-of-progress/0000018e-bf65-d480-a99e-ff77153b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡审判的关键证人拿执法部门开玩笑。现在他正在付出代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/key-witness-in-netanyahu-trial-made-a-joke-of-law-enforcement-now-hes-paying-the-price/0000018e-bf19-d6f4-afaf-bf5b478e0000</link><description>什洛莫·菲尔伯在代表国家作证之前就明确表明了他的忠诚所在。在检察官宣布计划取消与他的协议后，下一步就是对他提出指控</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 20:24:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/key-witness-in-netanyahu-trial-made-a-joke-of-law-enforcement-now-hes-paying-the-price/0000018e-bf19-d6f4-afaf-bf5b478e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列迷失了方向，内塔尼亚胡不知道他要把我们带到哪里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-08/ty-article/.highlight/israel-is-lost-and-netanyahu-has-no-idea-where-hes-taking-us/0000018e-be71-d480-a99e-fe77a9cf0000</link><description>当我的导航应用程序被以色列军队的 GPS 干扰器弄得毫无用处时，我突然意识到，我在路上感受到的不安全和不确定感与 10 月 7 日以来的全国情绪完全一致</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 18:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-08/ty-article/.highlight/israel-is-lost-and-netanyahu-has-no-idea-where-hes-taking-us/0000018e-be71-d480-a99e-fe77a9cf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家检察官表示将撤销在内塔尼亚胡审判中与关键证人达成的协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-attorney-says-it-will-revoke-agreement-with-key-witness-in-netanyahu-trial/0000018e-becd-d480-a99e-fedfb5c00000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的心腹、政府 4000 号案件的关键证人什洛莫·菲尔伯 (Shlomo Filber) 在出庭作证时未能遵守协议条款。在作证期间，菲尔伯撤回了他之前提出的几项主张，导致检察官要求法庭宣布他为敌对证人</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 18:07:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-attorney-says-it-will-revoke-agreement-with-key-witness-in-netanyahu-trial/0000018e-becd-d480-a99e-fedfb5c00000</guid></item><item><title>“他们无缘无故朝我肚子开枪”：以色列青少年讲述在加沙被囚禁的经历</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/they-shot-me-in-the-stomach-for-no-reason-israeli-teen-recounts-captivity-in-gaza/0000018e-be4f-d8c8-afbe-feffb99e0000</link><description>11 月获释的利亚姆·奥尔 (Liam Or) 表示，直到获释那天，他才知道 10 月 7 日发生了什么，而且他和在新星节上被劫持的人质奥马尔 (Omer) 相信他们是唯一的以色列人质</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 17:39:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/they-shot-me-in-the-stomach-for-no-reason-israeli-teen-recounts-captivity-in-gaza/0000018e-be4f-d8c8-afbe-feffb99e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 185 天：白宫称向哈马斯提出新的休战提案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-185-new-truce-proposal-presented-to-hamas-white-house-says/0000018e-be79-d480-a99e-fe7fc2490001</link><description>外国外交官对协议表示“谨慎乐观”；哈马斯否认取得进展 ■ 本格维尔：如果内塔尼亚胡在没有拉法行动的情况下结束战争，内塔尼亚胡将失去总理职位 ■ 外国记者协会呼吁以色列“不受限制地进入加沙” ■ 以色列国防军：士兵射杀了试图刺伤的巴勒斯坦妇女他们在约旦河西岸检查站 ■ 伊朗外长表示“未来的日子对以色列来说将是艰难的” ■ 战争已过去 185 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 16:56:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-185-new-truce-proposal-presented-to-hamas-white-house-says/0000018e-be79-d480-a99e-fe7fc2490001</guid></item><item><title>迈达斯王逆转：本杰明·内塔尼亚胡、加沙战争和价值毁灭的艺术</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/king-midas-in-reverse-benjamin-netanyahu-the-gaza-war-and-the-art-of-value-destruction/0000018e-bdb4-de0c-a3cf-fff668dd0000</link><description>在外交上，10月7日之后，以色列在加沙对抗哈马斯的战争中一切顺利。然后内塔尼亚胡的傲慢、管理不善和不诚实的无能接管了一切</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 16:10:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/king-midas-in-reverse-benjamin-netanyahu-the-gaza-war-and-the-art-of-value-destruction/0000018e-bdb4-de0c-a3cf-fff668dd0000</guid></item><item><title>外国记者协会呼吁以色列取消对加沙独立媒体的禁令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/foreign-press-association-calls-on-israel-to-lift-ban-on-independent-press-in-gaza/0000018e-be21-d92b-adaf-fe6513ea0000</link><description>FPA董事会表示，是否前往加沙实地的决定应由每个国际媒体自行决定，全面禁令限制了世界目睹战争给各方带来的真正代价的能力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 15:18:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/foreign-press-association-calls-on-israel-to-lift-ban-on-independent-press-in-gaza/0000018e-be21-d92b-adaf-fe6513ea0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日加沙战争六周年纪念日，全球各地举行集会和抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/rallies-protests-held-across-the-globe-on-six-month-anniversary-of-oct-7-war-in-gaza/0000018e-bdcb-db65-a7af-fdcba4940000</link><description>周日，前人质、人质家属和领导人向拥挤的人群发表了讲话，这是自 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以色列以来半年的日子</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 15:03:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/rallies-protests-held-across-the-globe-on-six-month-anniversary-of-oct-7-war-in-gaza/0000018e-bdcb-db65-a7af-fdcba4940000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔任命新警察局长，因滥用职权和违反信任而接受调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-picks-new-police-chief-who-was-investigated-for-abusing-powers-breach-of-trust/0000018e-be20-d6f4-afaf-be62f23a0000</link><description>2015年，时任警察局长阿尔谢奇拒绝了内部调查部门拒绝阿夫沙洛姆·佩莱德晋升的建议。警方消息人士称佩莱德为“本-格维尔的傀儡”，两人的关系可以追溯到十多年前</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 14:44:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-picks-new-police-chief-who-was-investigated-for-abusing-powers-breach-of-trust/0000018e-be20-d6f4-afaf-be62f23a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>